        <abstract>
            <p>Sends Mrs Barber’s address.</p> 
<p>Gratified that CD hates Owen. Hopes Owen will not answer <hi rend="italic">Nature</hi> letter and draw JDH into controversy. Owen’s letter was not intended for Ayrton to use. Its appearance must have horrified him.</p> 
            <p>State of Huxley’s health makes JDH uneasy.</p>
            <p>Willy is in a stockbroker’s office in London and likes it.</p>
        </abstract>
